As per Rule 114AAA, a person shall face the following consequences if his PAN has become
inoperative due to non-linking with Aadhaar. These consequences shall take effect from 01-07-
2023 and continue till the PAN becomes operative:
(a) The tax shall be deducted at a higher rate in accordance with Section 206AA;
(b) The tax shall be collected at a higher rate in accordance with Section 206CC;
